  "text": "To test the remaining hypotheses we use multinomial logit models estimating the likelihood of a patent to be assigned to the alternative categories, with university assignment as the base category (cf. Della Malva et al., forthcoming; [CITATION_1] . Given the small number (83) of patents jointly owned by a university and a non-profit organization (group 6), these are dropped from the analysis.",
